{"tid":110153,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港仔試食）天水圍屋企水喉清水","createTime":"2017-02-06T13:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T15:26:13.000Z","uid":1582,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8e048faa002d9fb0edbd0c1329b127862e323b","tid":110153,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:11:57.000Z","msg":"今日day Off毒在家中 點知檯面冇晒嘢飲 所以決定坐電腦凳去屋企廚房嗰個水龍頭攞）外賣返檯面食<br />\n今次買咗：<br />\n清水X1<br />\n送1/3個水樽既水<br />\n合共$0<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oitu1Ke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foitu1Ke.jpg&h=ed55c188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先講下杯清水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bGL0v6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bGL0v6.jpg&h=242546de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面有Hydrogen同Oxygen 水多到滿瀉 水用大量氯氣消毒過 清而無味 不過略嫌多同凍咗d<br />\n入面有水 有d清水味 飲落唔會覺dry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住到水樽水<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/211141_5264d5ca7b506949b255685f2317a193.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F211141_5264d5ca7b506949b255685f2317a193.jpg&h=ff932218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樽蓋有d膠<br />\n內餡以水同空氣為主 得少少水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過幾潤幾正 鐘意飲水嘅朋友可以試吓<br />\n<br />\n總括而言 味道唔錯 東江水價格昂貴 如果得閒想試吓唔同水味可以去飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff61b3a3d71ec6c55fcfad8a8bf34cd06aa42fc","tid":110153,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:18:45.000Z","msg":"幽默感呢樣野無得勉強架..."},{"pid":"a8f02e1d5bbfccfdb84cd39d9cadcbfbf90d80a3","tid":110153,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25a49289fd73ebcb2995f180257fc8675c1f75b5","tid":110153,"uid":15757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0